Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell with the mask you wore yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nono, if it's not too weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going to leave it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you look better this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I-is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll do it then!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chouka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how do you think I look today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are more beautiful than anyone once again,\Nand you smell lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Merci, Chouka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...let's head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:52.15,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,0)\blur1.5\pos(480.3,889.2)\}Episode 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:52.15,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,0)\blur1.5\pos(1305.9,889.2)\fscx80}Notes on a Scandal
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Outrageous! There's something wrong with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked so cool when he stepped up\Nto fight in the Warabimpics!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally saw him in a different light\Nafter he won against that big bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These haiku techniques are called\Nbutsumei, oriku, and kutsukaburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time of the Shin Kokin Wakashu,\Nhaikus got even more complicated, with yaedasugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to the teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to your own classrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness. I've got to be vigilant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making that shrill sound every time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, every last one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I thought I heard something else\Namongst the cheers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You bastard, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? To eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be allowing us to\Naccompany you then, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating's the only time I get a little freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two, you're puttin'\Na lot of pressure on me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.29,0:05:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what would happen to you\Nif our glares weren't working?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.62,0:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All the girls wanting to speak with you\Nwould rush at you all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain of bein' popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let this get to your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, you two, if you keep makin' that face\Nall the time, it ain't gonna make you cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially when...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault do you think this is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll come for you tomorrow morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.08,0:05:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He never noticed my uniform was different\Nfrom what I usually wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:06:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He should have said something about\Nmy different perfume today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching a while,\Nbut I'm still surprised he's won them over this bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At first I'd thought he was just like\Nall the other violent delinquents, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's completely hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Exceedingly hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let this get to his head like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have never given him\Nyour stamp so easily, Rin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but you gave him yours, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.21,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I hit my head extremely hard back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I had a high fever and my mind was hazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:07:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to do something about him\Nbefore things around here take a turn for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we should take this to the next level,\Nand attempt to correct him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we don't have to go that--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it could be what he needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He should go through that horrible experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.46,0:07:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothin', just had a really bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I eat too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm crazy tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you gonna do about showering?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, not today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Too sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sup, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're actually waiting for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to pull?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I just slept so well last night,\NI woke up in an awesome mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Your usual uniform looks\Nway better on you, Onigawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-- you bastard, you'd noticed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You went back to your old perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The one yesterday was good,\Nbut this smell's definitely you, Kikakujo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's get this day started!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Started with a big bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hold it just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,C-c'mon, Rin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?! Umm, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't had your inspection yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll try correcting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...him tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oui! It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What'd you find?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I trusted you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Onigawara? Are you crying right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a fool to trust you even for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Rin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.40,0:10:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.21,0:10:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?! Don't you have an explanation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Salope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no memory of this even...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Onigawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura Fudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is with that picture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl in it's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaba Satori, one of the Five Swords, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is seriously not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really gonna kill m-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.04,0:11:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You should walk on the sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break! I don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That fast little bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.58,0:11:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Kyo-bo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe you've managed\Nto win Kyo-bo's heart, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(618,793.001)\bord4.5\blur4.5}Female
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:12:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are so naive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And how very resourceful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Tamaba do\Nsomething like this in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.29,0:12:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your strong point, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If she took you out, Princess Oni and\NPrincess Kikakujo wouldn't shut up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.88,0:12:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she's trying to\Nwreck your relationships with them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say, if those two don't realize\Nthey're being tricked, Satori can plot all she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.88,0:12:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I? No really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.38,0:12:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered one thing very clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not have a boner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.63,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a big ray of light covering up\Nthe important bits in the photo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you get the original data,\Nyou can provide the others with an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm gonna go with.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you're going to\Nsneak into the girls' dorm again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.80,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the disturbance you caused last time,\Nthe traps have intensified tenfold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're found there,\Nthey'll send you straight to the torture room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it. That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot possibly sneak in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if I can't sneak in...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Buri-buri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out! Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that picture about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When did it happen?! How do you know her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we've beat him this much,\Nand he hasn't made a peep!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Buri-buri! Buri-buri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Buri-bu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him down. Take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that horrible scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They really did a number on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I brought you some dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Something dry? Man, you're thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Got enough water in me to bathe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My goodness. You truly like to do insensible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.86,0:15:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't sneak in, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. If I can't get in, I'll get them to let me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, I just let them catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done. I'll take part in this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You sayin' you're gonna help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the reason, Princess Satori\Nis taking unreasonable action,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I do not find it funny in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:16:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura! You've done well to appear before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better be ready for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, this kind of unreasonable action isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.92,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Had some reasons to go through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll go on by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.83,0:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We've both boarded this ship. I will accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's gonna be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.67,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And if anything happened to you, she'd be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can't say I'm not happy for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Satori is not in her quarters at present.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to search through her things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, let's get moving and\Nstart sifting through her secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is now the time for this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have given it to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the masked girls from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I don't know just how many\Nof those masked girls there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's hard to point one out specifically.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a chance they are\Nkeeping it on their body as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we won't know unless we meet 'em face to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, perhaps not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Princess Satori is in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not the time to make lewd faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Satori is a strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She behaves like a mysterious creature\Npretending to be a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretending to be a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's strange to say that, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you they've increased the traps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is way overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, Hanasaka-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,C-can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Her boobs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If they find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...but if we don't line up early, they'll all be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it's kinda serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go buy some tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.21,0:19:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-nothing, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt like I heard a guy's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kinda cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.42,0:19:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.92,0:19:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.79,0:19:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that little thing be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We got away some--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what was with that little cub?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I haven't told everyone yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's the cub Kyo-bo gave birth to this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Its name is Do-mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo's a married woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, more to you than meets the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I was this close to\Ntroddin' on another man's territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop your insolence!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyo-bo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Madam! How improper! This is really gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she might have sewn it into her underwear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up? Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Satori's sword is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten... su... metsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Misogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Misogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.25,0:21:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of all the masked girls, it is said that she\Nis the right hand of Princess Satori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her weapon's... a short bamboo stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Hanasaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure who you are fighting for,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have my own reasons to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, never expected a ranged technique\Nto come flying like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:30.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\pos(973.999,675)}Blowgun Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.24,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you did come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.28,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But wowie, I'm surprised that Warabi's working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The mysterious creature...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't tell what people will do, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Omugi here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.70,0:23:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiko here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw some buri-buri today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.42,0:23:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Buri-buri is a torture technique where you\Nhang someone upside down and spin them around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.50,0:23:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and whack them with thick rattan canes\Nwhile shouting "buri-buri!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't hit you with leather strops in buri-buri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, you use that for it\Nand you deserve to be buri-buri'd!
